title: Podunk Arkansas
description: these guys a one of my favorite bands.i got this disc from the guitarist jon.he burned it for me and sent it to my house,really cool guy!he said to "burn a copy for any one who might enjoy their silly songs",so here they are.you can look them up on myspace and check them out and hear a few tracks(last i checked they had stoner ghost and mickey D's on there,i think a few more.).if you've ever seen the troma flick slaughter party then you've heard them(i know there is not a large following of slaughter party fans out there.i assure you the music is great!)i couldn't ever find their music to buy or download,now you can download it free because of the awesomeness that is jon!thanks and enjoy!
